ActFisheries Act
SubjectRegulations Amending the Fishery (General) Regulations
PrecisRegulations amending the FISHERY (GENERAL) REGULATIONS in order to (1) prescribe a group of major fish stocks; and (2) ensure that rebuilding plans for prescribed stocks are developed consistently and within a reasonable time to encourage successful rebuilding.
